edia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an outlier\", \"from\": 5282, \"to\": 5292}, {\"ngram\": \"terms\", \"from\": 5296, \"to\": 5301}, {\"ngram\": \"morphological characteristics.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\", \"from\": 5305, \"to\": 5338}, {\"ngram\": \"both ferocity\", \"from\": 5369, \"to\": 5382}, {\"ngram\": \"poetry\", \"from\": 5387, \"to\": 5393}, {\"ngram\": \"motion\", \"from\": 5397, \"to\": 5403}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His stroke technique is impeccable, and his underwater work might be the best in the world at this point.\", \"from\": 5406, \"to\": 5511, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His stroke technique\", \"from\": 5406, \"to\": 5426}, {\"ngram\": \"his underwater work\", \"from\": 5446, \"to\": 5465}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 5487, \"to\": 5496}, {\"ngram\": \"this point\", \"from\": 5500, \"to\": 5510}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the crucial 15 meters at the starts and turns when swimmers are allowed to be submerged, Marchand blows away his competition.\", \"from\": 5512, \"to\": 5640, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the crucial 15 meters\", \"from\": 5515, \"to\": 5536}, {\"ngram\": \"the starts\", \"from\": 5540, \"to\": 5550}, {\"ngram\": \"swimmers\", \"from\": 5566, \"to\": 5574}, {\"ngram\": \"Marchand\", \"from\": 5604, \"to\": 5612}, {\"ngram\": \"his competition\", \"from\": 5624, \"to\": 5639}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There are greater drag forces on the surface than beneath it, so the work down below is critical.\", \"from\": 5641, \"to\": 5738, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"greater drag forces\", \"from\": 5651, \"to\": 5670}, {\"ngram\": \"the surface\", \"from\": 5674, \"to\": 5685}, {\"ngram\": \"the work\", \"from\": 5706, \"to\": 5714}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cL\\u00c3\\u00a9on is much, much better than anyone else underwater,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Peterson says.\", \"from