ake\", \"from\": 6206, \"to\": 6219}, {\"ngram\": \"water\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094which\", \"from\": 6235, \"to\": 6248}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some of this may simply come down to good genes.\", \"from\": 6290, \"to\": 6338, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"good genes\", \"from\": 6327, \"to\": 6337}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Marchand is the son of two French Olympic swimmers, Xavier and C\\u00c3\\u00a9line, which certainly helps account for body type and \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cfeel.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d But the other element that has to be present in addition to physical gifts is work ethic.\", \"from\": 6339, \"to\": 6560, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6366, \"end\": 6372, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9995195053585133, \"rank\": 0.0004718911713470928, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Marchand\", \"from\": 6339, \"to\": 6347}, {\"ngram\": \"the son\", \"from\": 6351, \"to\": 6358}, {\"ngram\": \"Xavier\", \"from\": 6391, \"to\": 6397}, {\"ngram\": \"C\\u00c3\\u00a9line\", \"from\": 6402, \"to\": 6409}, {\"ngram\": \"body type\", \"from\": 6445, \"to\": 6454}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cfeel.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\", \"from\": 6459, \"to\": 6470}, {\"ngram\": \"the other element\", \"from\": 6475, \"to\": 6492}, {\"ngram\": \"addition\", \"from\": 6519, \"to\": 6527}, {\"ngram\": \"physical gifts\", \"from\": 6531, \"to\": 6545}, {\"ngram\": \"work\", \"from\": 6549, \"to\": 6553}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Marchand has that in abundance.\", \"from\": 6561, \"to\": 6592, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Marchand\", \"from\": 6561, \"to\": 6569}, {\"ngram\": \"abundance\", \"from\": 6582, \"to\": 6591}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After selling himself to Bowman in a cold-call email, Marchand showed up at Arizona State as an accomplished swimmer bu