.org/resource/Arizona_State_University\", \"score\": 0.9989752579469701, \"rank\": 0.0006318848619053738, \"text\": \"ASU\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arizona_State_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arizona_State_University\"}, {\"begin\": 7443, \"end\": 7448, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ulysses_S._Grant\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.121766254414057e-18, \"text\": \"Grant\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ulysses_S._Grant\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ulysses_S._Grant\"}, {\"begin\": 7449, \"end\": 7454, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/House_music\", \"score\": 0.9999999997908162, \"rank\": 2.096299726833247e-10, \"text\": \"House\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/House_music\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/House_music\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"crazy practices.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\", \"from\": 7396, \"to\": 7415}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cEverybody\", \"from\": 7455, \"to\": 7467}, {\"ngram\": \"our practices\", \"from\": 7483, \"to\": 7496}, {\"ngram\": \"I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ve\", \"from\": 7513, \"to\": 7519}, {\"ngram\": \"three years\", \"from\": 7566, \"to\": 7577}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When he does it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s like, \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0098Oh my gosh, he\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s human after all.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d L\\u00c3\\u00a9on Marchand was standing underneath a maze of scaffolding underneath the stands in the arena when someone handed him a phone.\", \"from\": 7580, \"to\": 7780, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7658, \"end\": 7666, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\", \"score\": 0.9852987591724566, \"rank\": 0.014872137983238814, \"text\": \"Marchand\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q11774891\"], \"wikid\":